				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">"Creationism" can also refer to <a href="Creation_myth" title="Creation myth">creation myths</a>, or to a <a href="Creationism_(soul)" title="Creationism (soul)">concept about the origin of the soul</a>. For the movement in Spanish literature, see <a href="Creacionismo" title="Creacionismo">Creacionismo</a>.</div>
