<li id="cite_note-num-4"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-num_4-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-num_4-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-num_4-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-num_4-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a href="../Ronald_L._Numbers" title="Ronald L. Numbers" class="mw-redirect">Ronald L. Numbers</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.counterbalance.net/history/anticreat-frame.html">"Antievolutionists and Creationists"</a>. <i>Creationism History</i>. Counterbalance Meta-Library<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.counterbalance.net/history/anticreat-frame.html">http://www.counterbalance.net/history/anticreat-frame.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2007-08-15</span>.</span></span></li>
